Class Proj4CoordSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.CoordSystem
      • com.mousebird.maply.Proj4CoordSystem

  • public class Proj4CoordSystem
extends CoordSystem
    A wrapper around the Proj4 general scheme for coordinate systems. You set this up with a string that Proj4 recognizes and it will pass that directly through and use it.
